### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### List accounts (default to first company if companyId not provided)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts

### List accounts for specific company
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts?companyId=default-company-id

### Create account (without companyId - uses default)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "1010",
  "name": "Petty Cash",
  "type": "ASSET"
}

### Create account (with companyId)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": "default-company-id",
  "code": "2100",
  "name": "Short-term Loans",
  "type": "LIABILITY"
}

